OL,3,CJobs market cools further over
OL,4,Ceconomic concerns and rising costs
OL,6,FHiring activity fell further in July
OL,7,Fas the UK jobs market was weighed down
OL,8,Fby concerns over the economic outlook
OL,9,Fand increased labour costs, according
OL,10,Fto new figures.
OL,12,FGrowth in starting salaries also
OL,13,Fslowed to its lowest level for more
OL,14,Fthan four years as firms tightened
OL,15,Ftheir recruitment budgets.
OL,17,FThe monthly KPMG and REC report on
OL,18,Fjobs showed a "further steep decline"
OL,19,Fin permanent staff appointment in July.
