OL,3,CJobs market cools further over
OL,4,Ceconomic concerns and rising costs
OL,6,FThe influential report showed a
OL,7,Freading of 40.0 for permanent
OL,8,Fplacements in the UK, improving
OL,9,Fslightly from 39.1 in June.
OL,11,FHowever, any figure below 50
OL,12,Frepresents decline in the job market,
OL,13,Fwith levels over 50 showing growth.
OL,14,FThe data therefore indicated another
OL,15,Fmonth of contraction.
OL,17,FJon Holt, group chief executive and UK
OL,18,Fsenior partner at KPMG, said: "The
OL,19,Flabour market cooled in July as chief
OL,20,Fexecs held back from increasing their
OL,21,Frecruitment budgets.
