OL,3,CJobs market cools further over
OL,4,Ceconomic concerns and rising costs
OL,6,F"Economic uncertainty, the
OL,7,Fcomplexities of AI adoption and global
OL,8,Fheadwinds are all weighing on business
OL,9,Fplanning."
OL,11,FRecruiters frequently said in the
OL,12,Fsurvey that weak confidence about the
OL,13,Feconomy and "increases in payroll
OL,14,Fcosts" were factors causing the drop
OL,15,Fin hiring.
OL,17,FIt pointed towards a "steady" jobs
OL,18,Fmarket in certain sectors, such as
OL,19,Fengineering, but flagged a continued
OL,20,Fdrop in hiring in retail and
OL,21,Fhospitality.
