OL,3,CJobs market cools further over
OL,4,Ceconomic concerns and rising costs
OL,6,FMeanwhile, starting salary inflation
OL,7,Fslowed for a second month in a row to
OL,8,Fits lowest level since March 2021.
OL,10,FThe data comes after the Bank of
OL,11,FEngland pointed towards slowing wage
OL,12,Fgrowth over the coming year while the
OL,13,Funemployment rate could tick higher.
OL,15,FKate Shoesmith, REC deputy chief
OL,16,Fexecutive, said: "There is a path to
OL,17,Fjobs market recovery ` but it will
OL,18,Ftake co-ordinated action from
OL,19,FGovernment, the Bank of England and
OL,20,Fbusinesses to maximise on any
OL,21,Fpotential upswing.
