OL,6,F"With starting salaries and temporary
OL,7,Fpay rising only modestly, it was right
OL,8,Fto cut interest rates last week.
OL,10,F"More action like this, to stabilise
OL,11,Fthe business cost-base, is what will
OL,12,Fsupport growth and boost the jobs
OL,13,Fmarket this year."
